snippet.textDisplay:
I don't know why there's a such thing as a dance line. I know it's there to represent the best dancers of the group but I don't find it reasonable at all because every member is equally good.
In my opinion Yoongi, Namjoon and Seokjin are just as good as the dance line. I won't deny Hoseok is the best dancer in the group, but each member is unique in their own way and dances amazingly. I don't mean to say that having a dance line isn't okay, it's just that it's not fair to point out a specific member and say they're good while the others aren't.

I mean —come on, did you even see Joon, Yoongi and Jin's fancams individually?! There isn't a difference! They're just as good as Hoseok but just with different vibes and uniqueness.

Don't fight with me on this, if your a true ARMY you would know what I'm talking about about. I'm not trying to be aggressive, neither putting down Jungkook, Jimin, Taehyung and Hobi and praising just Joon, Yoongi and Seokjin. I love all the members very much, and it breaks my heart to see others comparing them like that. It's not fair! I get so mad when some ARMYs are like "wow Taehyung is so good! Jin isn't even close!". And you can yourself a ARMY?

Anyways thank you for reading, hope you understand 𑁍♡𑁍
Saranghae ~♡♡♡
